Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:33.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
